    "implementation": "hybrid",
    "rationale": "Filled and soft surfaces have a base fill and use OKLCH L-delta state shifts. Outline, dotted, ghost, and link variants are transparent and use state overlay tokens. Figma overlays are a visual simulation for filled/soft, not the exact code implementation.",
    "available": [
